{"id": "1431081428636008571", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "トゥルーの、というよりパーティー全体の会心やダメ強が触腕に影響した、と記憶しています！なのでトゥルー一人でがんばって率盛る！というよりはPT内で上げれたら上げるみたいな感じかなと　自分はトゥルーの密約サブステはダメ強、死亡抵抗、会心を意識して厳選してます", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T00:46:40.794000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1212352584380321823"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1430901565283106868", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431081514313056266", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "722017209182060635", "author_name": "esukun125", "author_bot": false, "content": "(間違ってたらすみません🙇)", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T00:47:01.221000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431138700363956254", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "855125638407389224", "author_name": "youmouseishimenawa", "author_bot": false, "content": "魔風瓶をいい加減使おうかなと思ってるのですが、誰を取るべきでしょうか？\n現在の未入手キャラはこの8人です\nまた、恒常召喚の石も貯まって来ているのですが、何を引くべきなのでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T04:34:15.438000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1431138700166696981", "filename": "IMG_996A72734F91-1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 351937, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1431138700166696981/IMG_996A72734F91-1.jpg?ex=6a341e07&is=6a32cc87&hm=eb40839bbabbeea18d580706f0c74c58a1d008ce3a53cbe118889568c1e56ae5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431157219390652478", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "ずっと言われてるけど、バランス調整がしばしば入るので恒常については「モチベが続くように好みでどうぞ」\n恒常石も同じで、推しが恒常落ちする未来まで溜めとくのもいい\n現時点での戦力ＵＰを求めるなら\n・伸ばしたい陣営\nか\n・頭数が足りない陣営\nを回すと良いと思う", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T05:47:50.718000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431157397019168778", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "ガチャ回してから伸ばしたい子に瓶つっこむのがいいとは思いますね", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T05:48:33.068000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431157602615558165", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "現状のエンドコンテンツの完全踏破には19～20キャラ、サブコンテンツのクリアには各陣営２キャラはいるので･･･", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T05:49:22.086000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431165375445336135", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "1146730063006548039", "author_name": "statice_11", "author_bot": false, "content": "そうなんですね！？細かくありがとうございます！参考にさせていただきます！", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T06:20:15.273000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["722017209182060635"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "M_satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431081428636008571", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431166291518947401", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "例えばピックでトゥルーやマーフィーどちらか引いてるなら深海の恒常も揃える〜とか、ソレール引いたから〜とかピック基準で考えると良いよ", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T06:23:53.682000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431166463569563690", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "438289046993633281", "author_name": "iihige", "author_bot": false, "content": "ぼくはジェンキンが好きだから開始日からずっと超次元しか引かなかったせいで課金してるくせにキャラコンプしてない", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T06:24:34.702000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431181580529041509", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "855125638407389224", "author_name": "youmouseishimenawa", "author_bot": false, "content": "引き当てたソレールが好みなのでずーっと狂魔引いてるんですけどなんか他の陣営と合わせた方がいいとも聞くしでまだよくわかってないです", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:24:38.866000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431182240309837906", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "855125638407389224", "author_name": "youmouseishimenawa", "author_bot": false, "content": "凸の段階進めるかとも思いましたがどれがどんくらい強いかとか見当もつかないのでなんかぼんやりとガチャを引いてます", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:27:16.170000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431183274541318197", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "・凸は３凸まで（◆が３つ並ぶまで）はスキル強化が入るので明確に強いです、それ以降は愛だと思っていいです\n・基本的には陣営は単染めの方が強いです（扱いにくいなどの理由が混ぜる理由の大半）\n・例えば超次元はカードを出し入れできるので、明確なキーカードのあるＰＴに混ぜると強いです\n・深海＋狂魔は防御が高い＋回復ができる、組み合わせなので耐久に向く、などの感じです", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:31:22.750000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["855125638407389224"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431182240309837906", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431183566984712193", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "単染めすると各陣営の特殊能力に対するボーナス値が激増します（＝混ぜるとボーナスが激減する）", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:32:32.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431183746190807101", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "４つの陣営のうち自分が扱いやすいと感じるものを軸に覚えておくといいかと", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:33:15.200000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431184315466645615", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "247960263599325186", "author_name": "sergeant_aoi", "author_bot": false, "content": "ここにチュートリアルがあるはず", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:35:30.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1431184315223638036", "filename": "IMG_1980.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 434581, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1431184315223638036/IMG_1980.png?ex=6a344882&is=6a32f702&hm=1585d2d9f0d879392918fe2bda469eea27ff16c9c48c432c68e0f4660a5795b2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431186284432457790", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 0, "author_id": "855125638407389224", "author_name": "youmouseishimenawa", "author_bot": false, "content": "ずーっとソレール軸の狂魔単ですね私\nわかりやすいです", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T07:43:20.364000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1431196309590904944", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "type": 19, "author_id": "797509921343275038", "author_name": "8106ne", "author_bot": false, "content": "染めでもいいと思います。\n\nただ狂は染めの恩恵が低い方なので、耐えにしんどさ出てきたら深海と今世にすると少し楽になったりします", "timestamp": "2025-10-24T08:23:10.548000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["855125638407389224"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1431186284432457790", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
